name: Ma'rufah
greetingText: I know i av let u down a lot buh just want u to know that I love you and you mean so much to me!
wishText: Thank you for all the memories we have. Without you, the world would have been colorless to me I love you so much thanks for being there amd also for coming into my life happy birthday Adebayo Titilayo Ma'rufah!🎈🎈🎈🎈🎈🎈🎈! ;)
